[Location]
What is ‘Safe Drop’? A ‘Safe Drop’ is when our delivery team member finds a suitable place at your address where they can safely leave an item that does not require a signature.
You can find out more about Safe Drop locations here: https://auspost.com.au/receiving/manage-deliveries-in- transit/leave-in-a-safe-place
If you are still unable to locate your item, we recommend you contact your sender to see if they can assist further.
For future deliveries, you may like to find out about alternative delivery options by visiting https://auspost.com.au/receiving/mypost
